description: Starting near Lac Du Rocher parking, follow inter-centre trail to Monatgne Blanche top.  Incredible view point on Laurentian area. Then we go to check the shelter at Lac de l'Appel. A must.  Have a nice trek.  Tourlou!
directions: Exit #89 on 15N autoroute, go right to 329 North to St-Donat, left Ch. Val des Lacs, right Ch. du Lac de L'Orignal, left to Ch. de Michaudville and left to Ch. du Lac `Du Rocher to parking.  (Just follow signs to Lac Du Rocher)
title: Montagne Blanche
